Success Criteria
Functional:

[ ] Win+Space triggers overlay from anywhere
[ ] Overlay appears above all windows (including fullscreen)
[ ] All four screens functional
[ ] Window tracking accurate
[ ] Calendar integration works
[ ] Focus modes mute notifications
[ ] App/file launching instant
Performance:

[ ] Overlay opens in < 300ms
[ ] Memory usage < 50MB
[ ] Smooth animations (60fps)
[ ] No lag or stuttering
User Experience:

[ ] Native OS feel
[ ] Intuitive navigation
[ ] Smooth transitions
[ ] Professional appearance
---

Risk Mitigation
Technical Risks:

[ ] Fullscreen overlay may fail in some games → Fallback to windowed mode detection
[ ] Notification control may be limited → Focus on app-level control
[ ] Calendar API rate limits → Implement caching
Business Risks:

[ ] User adoption → Focus on UX
[ ] Competition → Unique value proposition
[ ] Platform changes → Stay updated with Windows updates
---

